quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,84,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo: "Men gom…óinii Alla Rewetee…óo, men …óoftike Mo e kon ko O Yamiri men, men gom…óinii on wahyu jippinaa…óo e amen, e kon ko jippii e dow Ibraahiima e Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, e kon ko jippinaa e dow Annabaa…ďe …ďen immorde e ge…óal…ďe Yaaquuba, e kon ko Muusaa e Iisaa e Annabaa…ďe …ďen denndaangal okkaa immorde e Defte e Aayeeje Iw…óe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Men serndataa hakkunde ma…ď…ďe gom…óingol yoga yedda yoga, menen ko men jebbilanii…ďe Alla Tan"."
  3,85,"Kala …óa…ď…ďu…óo diina goo ko woori Diina kan (diina lislaamu) ka Alla Welanaa mo; Alla Ja…ďaŇčtaa mo kan, on …óon ka laakara, ko jeyaa…óo e hayru…ďe naatoo…ďe yiite …ďen."
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yim…ďe e gom…óingol Mo KaŇčko e Nulaa…óo Makko on; yeddu…ďe …ďaawo nde …ďe gom…óinnde Alla …ďe seeditoo wonnde kon ko Nulaa…óo Muhammadu jom kisiyee addi ko goonga, e wonnde …ďanngannduyeeji …óin arii hi…ói goongina …óum?! Alla Fewnataa e gom…óinal Makko ngal, …ďen yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe su…ďii…ďe majjere seli peewal."
  3,87,"Njo…ďdi …ďen too√Īoo…ďe su…ďii…ďe mehre nden, ko no fawii …ďe kuddi Alla ndin e Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďe …ďe denndaangal; …ďen ko wo…ó…óinaa…ďe ra…óaa…ďe e Yumeende Alla nden."
  3,88,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe ka yiite …ďe yaltataa, …ďe hayfinaŇčtaake lepte magge, …ďe wonaali nennaŇčtee…ďe fii no …ďe tuubira …ďe ngaŇčtinoo."
  3,89,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe ruttii …ďaawo keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe e too√Īe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mo∆ī∆īini golle ma…ď…ďe …óen; pellet, Alla ko Haforanoowo tuuboowo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Anndu…óo …ďe."
  3,90,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe, …ďe duumii e keeferaaku haa …ďe maayi e mu'un, …ďe ja…ďntaake tuubuubuyee tuma …ďe maayata; sabu haray laawike. Ko …ďen …óon woni majju…ďe laawol foccingol jottinoowol ka Alla ngol."
  3,91,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi e keeferaaku, hay gooto e ma…ď…ďe ja…ďaŇčtaake emmbere leydi ndin tew kaŇčŇče; hay si o soktorii …óen kaŇčŇče yaltugol ka yiite. ∆Āen …óon, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe, …ďe alaa walloo…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal ko no du√Īana …ďe lepte …óen."